function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	--Play Victory Music Stinger
	Hydra.MusicOverride(WORLD_SANC, "Music_Boss_Duriel_Victory")
end

function Start()
	if not playersAreReadyForBoss() then
		Hydra.EventSend("QST_VGN_Kehj_Caldeum_01B_DurielBoss_Abandoned")
		return
	end 
	
	if durielHasBeenAttempted() then
		Hydra.Wait(.25)
		local nTimeToModify = 1 - Hydra.QuestTimerGetTimeRemaining()
		Hydra.QuestTimerModifyTime(nTimeToModify)
	end
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	if not durielHasBeenAttempted() and playersAreReadyForBoss() and PRD:Roll() then
		Hydra.EventSend("QST_VGN_Kehj_Caldeum_01B_DurielBoss_DurielUnburrow")
	end
end

function Start(flTimeRemaining)
	
	if playersAreReadyForBoss() then
		Hydra.EventSend("QST_VGN_Kehj_Caldeum_01B_DurielBoss_DurielUnburrow")
	else
		Hydra.EventSend("QST_VGN_Kehj_Caldeum_01B_DurielBoss_Abandoned")
	end
	
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

	Hydra.ActorEnable(ID_BOSS)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(ID_BOSS, BOSS_INTRO_POWER)
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyQueueStart(BOSS_LEVEL_AREA) 	--Manually Start Encounter
	
	if not durielHasBeenAttempted() then
		Hydra.SetGameVariableFlag(sVarDurielAlreadyAttempted)
	end
	
	--Play Victory Music Stinger
	Hydra.MusicOverride(WORLD_SANC,  "Music_Boss_Duriel_Phase1")
end

function Start()
	if (Hydra.BossEncounterIsInProgress(BOSS_LEVEL_AREA)) then
		Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyComplete(BOSS_LEVEL_AREA)
	end
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, sLevelAreaName)
	
	for i, playerID in pairs(Hydra.PlayerActors()) do
		GlobalScreenshake(playerID, "Heavy")
	end
	
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idSelf, 12)
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectDuration(idSelf, 5)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idSelf, EG_INTRO_ROCKS)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idSelf, EG_INTRO_DIRT)
	
	if not durielHasBeenAttempted() then
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(CONV_INTRO, idActorPlayer)
	end
	
	Hydra.EventSend("QST_VGN_Kehj_Caldeum_01B_DurielBoss_Start")
end

unk_c47e01a.value:
local function durielHasBeenAttempted()
	return Hydra.IsGameVariableSet(sVarDurielAlreadyAttempted)
end

local function playersAreReadyForBoss()
	for i, playerID in pairs(Hydra.PlayerActorsInLevelArea(BOSS_LEVEL_AREA)) do -- check to see if anyone is actually in the boss encounter
		if Hydra.ActorIsAlive(playerID) then
			return true
		end
	end
	
	return false
end
